Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.66,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,離れる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.89,0:21:15.76,JP-Main-up-8,Boss,0,0,0,,下ろせ　下ろせよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれどこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.24,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7Gで馬鹿でかくなったさやまこに無人島ができてな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.34,JP-Main-up-8,Boss,0,0,0,,下ろせ来て
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.33,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,あそこならそうそう出られない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.22,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,あんな何もねえとこやだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.65,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,私は善治郎のもとへ向かう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.42,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,この状況を良くする方法が見つかるかもしれん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもここは
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.69,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,私たちで自警団を作ることになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああそっか　武器あるし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ドクター私らと逆向きの旅だね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.07,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,このサイズだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.15,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,車にありったけの燃料を積んでも何日かかるか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,気をつけて　何あるかわかんないし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それは私らもだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.37,0:21:50.50,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,目的地への道のりとはそういうものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.74,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,だからこそ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.08,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,一歩を踏み出す勇気には価値がある
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.14,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ブレースレット　また作ったけ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,本当
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.29,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,学习到底是为了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:04.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一点也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:07.69,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,正是因为不懂才去学习的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:11.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香有时候也说些理解不能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你许了什么愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:22.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:23.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你许了什么愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.36,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:25.24,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,上啊 抚子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,打倒对方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:41.39,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,去啊 战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:44.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,打倒对方
Comment: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.87,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啥鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这肯定是刚才那群小人搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全挣不开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,话说他们发射了很多东西 比如导弹什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是什么点 是导弹 是导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,除此之外 还有迷你士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,砰砰朝我们开枪 痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但因为质量很小 所以威力也不大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:50.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比起这个 绳子呀怎么解开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.81,ZH-Main-up-8,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:57.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:15.01,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你们俩 到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,首先 把我们放开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.70,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,回答我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 放开我再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.59,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,那么 到你死之前都可以保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们从吾野来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.82,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:30.84,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野的人 也没有任何变化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也 再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.84,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我是问 吾野的大家是否还和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.18,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们虽然没有 但迟早会变成动物的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.99,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你们来这里 做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.77,ZH-Main-up-8,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们在找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为啥说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,难道不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,本来想一点点说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你这样我又不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全部都说出来 讨价还价的份都没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 让他们放开后再说话 我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你这样子大叔一点变通的余地都没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最开始 你那种态度就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是大叔我好不爽他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也好不爽啊 这臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.37,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,转起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啥啥啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等等会 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快点停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.23,ZH-Main-up-8,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,脸也好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:17.99,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.90,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,好吵啊 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.88,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,现在是我在质问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.44,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,别自顾自就拌起嘴来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.29,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你俩吵架 却说我坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,突然非常火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.49,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我才没火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.13,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,谁会跟一个小女孩发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.32,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我可是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.03,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,为什么队长要对一个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:34.50,ZH-Main-Down,Soldier,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.94,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.30,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你们说你们要找医生 吾野应该也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:41.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们在找刀客塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.82,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,为什么找刀客塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的朋友长了蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然拔下来了 但是很可能快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.73,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.62,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,那也是7G影响造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,绝对是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.39,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,果然 老板说的是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啥情况 刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.76,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我们立刻向上级汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,话都说完了放我们下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:06.02,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我并未做出过这样的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.92,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我们不能向外部来者泄露城市的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.57,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,这是我们「英明」的老板做的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.68,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,奉老板之命 明天 你们的骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:19.79,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,将会在狭山市立博物馆的曙光剑齿象骨架旁展出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,骨架是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,变成骨架的话说明已经死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是死刑啊 这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:29.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,放开我 你这豌豆大小的垃圾虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,电流正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,电压正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.35,ZH-Main-up-8,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,安东尼 快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 小晶她叫我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.28,ZH-Main-up-8,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好好好行行行 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶 怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实和静留 她们俩去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小晶一个人好孤独好无聊噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:52.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她们肯定很快就回来的 再稍微等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,她们俩人绝对会绕行 去偷吃米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以我也要和安东尼一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 检查结束前就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,安东尼 毛绒绒的好可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:12.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你的脸越来越变得可爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊敲 手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别这样 会出血的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,手链可是会断掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听听我的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:23.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,已经知道这个城镇里确实有个很好的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:29.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还有就是要找到对方 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:29.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,解开这个的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:32.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个还没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这件事才是最重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,期望越高 失望越大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是 难道就没好办法了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:42.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会等会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等一下 大姐姐等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,拜托你帮我们松绑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们并没有伤害你的意图
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们只是想找刀客塔 让其帮助我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.14,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,要是和你们说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.84,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老板会把我剥成骨架 然后展出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以那个老板是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.59,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,回答的话也会被做成骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那你根本不用靠近过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,难道你有理由必须这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:09.75,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我是这里的清洁工 负责清扫垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.15,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,要是不干净 也会被制成骨办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:12.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们也和你一起捡垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:16.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想放水 就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,刚刚就想要去上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在我忍不住了 要在这嘘嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把公园搞脏也是没办法的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也想要屙尿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,会把一切搞乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱可不管呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果你给我们松绑 我们绝对会搞定老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留的吾野柔术可是真的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也是了不得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:42.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要么帮我 要么骨办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者被尿一身 然后被做成骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你选
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 马上要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.09,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,好疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:52.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去干掉老板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是先去看看刀客塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.94,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,博士她 被老板拘留了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.92,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,所以首先 要求助于知晓博士藏身之地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,都没人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.53,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,毕竟有外出禁止令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:09.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以 刀客塔为什么被拘留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.35,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,这要从头开始讲起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:17.17,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我们大家的变化 听说大概率是7G事件所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:21.19,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,城市不断膨胀 然后突然逆向变得非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.39,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,在这其中 有一个居民将我们团结了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.61,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,那就是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.67,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,戈帕·诚·安斯特朗姆女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好强 无论工作还是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.82,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,大家推举诚老师为领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.48,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,除了大小以外 生活水平基本维持不变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.58,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,但是就在这时 老板出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.01,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老板很快就支配了这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.41,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,因为是领袖 便抓捕了诚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.15,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,然后把她监禁在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老板这么厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.21,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,最后居民们被分为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.00,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,服从老板的 即上等稻荷山市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.81,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,自由被剥夺的 下等稻荷山市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.43,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我们是下等稻荷山市民 全部都在管理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.94,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,完全是为了依靠基础设施而生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,基建和的中药煎药陶罐是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.71,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,这座城市中基地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.41,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,都是为了满足老板的癖好而强迫人为爱发电
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.87,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,大家都放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.52,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,但是 要是诚老师能够回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.91,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,或许能再一次 挺直腰板子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:17.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因此我们才在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.36,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.72,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.05,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,请告诉我们诚老师所在的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.35,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,作为曾经的上等市民 你们应该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,情报源绝对不要暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在在稻荷山公园
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,正在寻找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.08,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,为什么要去找医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.71,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是已经说过 小晶身上长了蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:07.19,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我知道蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.20,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,医生什么的我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稻荷山这应该有个医生在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.91,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.85,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是的 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:17.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子姐是不是有困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的脸写满了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,实际上 小晶我也是问题少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,身体逐渐扭曲变形动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.68,ZH-Main-up-8,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,咱要是有困难 无论何时玲实她都会来帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这可是让我肚子疼了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我没想到你真的会去「吃书」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,教科书已经用不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:39.59,ZH-Main-up-8,Akira,0,0,0,,是你把它撕烂吃掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我要和你绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哼 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.54,ZH-Main-Down,Boy A,0,0,0,,喂 你看什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.55,ZH-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,敲 好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.62,ZH-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,全都是汉字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我觉得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.01,ZH-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.34,ZH-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,你就想取笑西吾野在秩父线上而不在西武池袋线上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 你这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,对小晶做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是今天稍微晚了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回来之后要好好说她 笨得跟猪一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也一起说教说教她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,请务必这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.69,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,诚老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,山田 她们是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,之后再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们来帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:02.14,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你们这群人 在我的基地里想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:02.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不如说挺普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.14,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你们怎么跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不告诉你 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你再擅自模仿他们试试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.96,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我会把你头拔掉 弄得你乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自作主张的人是你才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:14.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我全都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.46,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等 好近 你想做啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我原本想为啥大家要遵从你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,原来只是体型较大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.85,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,既然知道就别说出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,老子最讨厌的就是蠢蠢活着的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老娘也是超级讨厌像你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.80,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,不是 你这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.87,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我比你更加更加更加讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.21,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你 快 摸什么鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.56,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快点攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.43,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.07,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这点伤痛算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.36,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,核水导弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咪西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.99,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不会上两次当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.83,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.61,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你们是想赦免博士 然后占领这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我绝对不会让你得逞的 笨蛋辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你难道是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:54.44,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:00.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:01.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你先去小晶那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:02.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.08,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.72,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快点向博士攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.30,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,攻击多次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,别让她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.36,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,攻击攻击攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,动作小玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,她们是稻荷山公园的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等救治好小晶 我马上去帮静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留她 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快看小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,医生来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.83,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,等会 我不是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:41.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你不是刀客塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我是科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那完全没用啊 你治不好她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.02,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,总而言之先告诉我发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有啥意义啊 你又不是医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,之前 她的屁股上长了蘑菇 拔掉之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就好像变成其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,身体越来越无法动弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.37,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.60,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,晶小姐你描述一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.92,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇拔出后身体除了变得沉重以外有没其它的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,脑袋里像是有风呼呼吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.29,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你们真的非常幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.45,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果是7G的原因 医生根本治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老师您能治好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.11,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.06,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,就算是科学家 研究的领域也有区分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.67,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,但是我参与了7G的研究 大概能推测出一二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.09,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.71,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老师您参与了7G
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.02,ZH-Main-Down,Man,0,0,0,,那么老板推翻博士您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:32.32,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,他们知道我的经历 以为这能够让城市恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我们认为当前所发生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.27,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,是被称为「7G脑波干涉」的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,7-11 啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.77,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,在7G的影响下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.46,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,人类的身体也会随着意识的认知发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.97,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,要是想要恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,说得更加明白点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.30,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是说 晶小姐的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:53.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,是因为意识到自己某些重要的东西和蘑菇一起被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那么如果把「思想」给加回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,吃点蘑菇或许会好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:57.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇 你们没带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,还要去东吾野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.62,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不用 我记得老板的屋里长的有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.25,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,蘑菇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.34,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果善治郎还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.63,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或许我们能够采取更好的应对方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 善治郎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.23,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吾野的 平善治郎先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你们为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.08,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那家伙还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还活着 但是变成搞笑担当了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:23.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeko,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.78,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,软绵绵 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.15,ZH-Main-Down,Surgeon,0,0,0,,软绵绵手术 准备开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.60,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.39,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,别站这里 继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.82,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快点走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.47,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎是我的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.42,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,总而言之现在最重要是晶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里是 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺的房间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:09.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你打算干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,判我死刑拿我骨头去装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,确实 这也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还能动的时候 可是不会觉得自己输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.10,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,对 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么要做这些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你这样只是恃强凌弱罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,基地 我喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:29.39,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,很帅是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,战斗机 直升机 还有各式各样的车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.01,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我虽然一直都很憧憬 但从未和别人提起过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.91,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,但我最初的时候也交到了一些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.59,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我说也想和他们一样在基地里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,然后就被笑爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.55,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,他们说 以你的头脑和运动神经当然是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.36,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,然后7G发生后 就来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.20,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,反正那群人只会认为你无聊至极疯狂愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.89,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,为什么你看起来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋 你有去过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.18,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你要去池袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:08.67,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,那里很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,比起在那个鬼地方 和我在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,行 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.87,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,顺带一提
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.84,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,如果你能留在这里 就放你的朋友走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留和蘑菇交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.68,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,都说了我最讨厌辣妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是时候放弃你的想法吧 矮穷挫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:37.44,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,闭嘴闭嘴闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,可恶的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.76,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺的基地绝对不会让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,教科书 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:16.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.59,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,目标命中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.14,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.46,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那样子的话可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:29.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.72,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等等等等会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:36.75,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你们这群笨蛋 快点帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:38.21,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快点帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已经吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,笨笨笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.77,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.51,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样下去的话小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这根本 不是小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,愤世嫉俗 晦涩难懂的这些傻瓜书籍没有被读过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那本书是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是你的 最喜欢东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:32.09,ZH-Main-up-8,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.25,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,最喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等等等会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:32.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:32.65,ZH-Main-up-8,Makoto,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:33.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.78,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或许这样会有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个时候咱原纸奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你干什么鬼笨蛋玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是虐待狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:45.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,萨德主义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,说白了就是性虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:49.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,对他人的身体施加虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在对对方全身造成痛苦的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:53.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,享受性兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:54.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不懂就去读萨德侯爵的书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但这对笨蛋来说根本看不懂罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我的龙彦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:05.20,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,这种书我只剩下一册了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,而且我还是保存用根本没读过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.66,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:15.76,ZH-Main-up-8,Boss,0,0,0,,放我下来 放我下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他要被去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.24,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G意外地把狭山湖变大成了个无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.34,ZH-Main-up-8,Boss,0,0,0,,快点放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.33,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那个地方几乎走不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我不想去鸟不拉屎的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.65,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我会去找善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.42,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或许能够找到方法来改善当前的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是这里呢
