Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.74,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.08,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,迈出第一步的勇气是有价值的
